question:
What is the output of the following code?

```java
class Box {
    int value;
    Box(int v) { value = v; }
    Box createNew(int v) {
        return new Box(v);
    }
}

public class Test {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Box b1 = new Box(10);
        Box b2 = b1.createNew(20);
        System.out.println(b1.value + " " + b2.value);
    }
}
```

What is the result of compiling and running this code?

```java
class Processor {
    private String data;
    Processor(String d) { data = d; }
    public Processor process() {
        data = "processed " + data;
        return this;
    }
    public String getData() { return data; }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Processor p = new Processor("input");
        String result = p.process().getData();
        System.out.println(result);
    }
}
```
